      <title>法國出版商拉加代爾執行長因法庭起訴而辭去高階主管職務</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/arnaud-lagardere-resign-executive-roles-due-court-indictment-2024-04-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法國出版集團Lagardere SA 董事長兼首席執行官阿諾·拉加代爾(Arnaud Lagardere) 週二表示，由於之前的法院起訴書他將提出上訴，該公司董事長兼首席執行官阿諾·拉加代爾( Arnaud Lagardere) 將不得不辭去高階主管職務。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/arnaud-lagardere-resign-executive-roles-due-court-indictment-2024-04-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 07:06:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
